# UI & Theme Consistency

## Theme tokens (never hardcode hex in screens)

| Token file | Use for |
|------------|---------|
| `@/theme/colors` | Shared palette (extends `@prime/ui`) |
| `@/theme/spacing` | `spacing.*`, `radius.*` |
| `@/theme/admin` | Admin accent, canvas, cards, badges |
| `@prime/ui` `typography` | Display, heading, body, label scales |

## Styling rules

- Use `StyleSheet.create` — no inline style objects
- Form labels: 12px, weight 600, `colors.textSecondary`, uppercase
- Inputs: 1px `colors.borderDefault` border, `radius.sm`, `spacing.sm` padding, `colors.surfaceWhite` background
- Error state: `colors.errorRed` border and helper text

## Role-specific accents

**Admin** (`apps/unified-app/src/screens/admin/`)

- Canvas: `adminColors.canvasBg`
- Cards: `adminColors.cardBg`
- Primary actions / active states: `adminColors.primary`
- Reuse `@/components/admin`: `FormField`, `SelectField`, `DateField`, `SectionCard`, `FilterChips`, `StatusBadge`, `KPICard`

**Customer / Officer**

- Accent: `colors.primaryNavy`
- Canvas: `colors.background`
- Reuse `@/components/common` and `@prime/ui` (`Screen`, `Button`, `EmptyState`)

## Lists & states

- Lists: `FlatList` with stable `keyExtractor` and memoized `renderItem`
- Every screen: loading, error, and empty states via `@/components/common`

## Sheets & modals

- Surface: `colors.surfaceWhite`
- Top corners: `radius.lg`
- Backdrop: `colors.overlay`
- Header: Cancel / title / Done row with `colors.borderDefault` divider

## Forms

- React Hook Form + Zod for all forms
- Use shared field components — do not build one-off inputs when a shared component exists
